      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Participants</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-demographics-target field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Participants (Demographics):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_demographics_target%3A112">General Public</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-demographics-target-other field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Other: Demographics:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">residents of the Rokko and North District area near Kobe</div><div class="field-item odd">Japan</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-public-roles-target field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Participants (Public Roles):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A128">Lay Public</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A130">Experts (e.g. Scientists, Engineers, Criminologists, Doctors, Lawyers)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A131">Elected Public Official</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-participant-selection field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Recruitment:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_participant_selection%3A31">Open to all with targeted recruitment</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-participant-select-other field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Other: Method of Recruitment:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">open to all who lived